  "synopsis": "With the Qianling Mausoleum destroyed and the Longquan Treasure missing, former prince Li Xingyun seeks to retire to the mountains. Bu Liang Shuai resolves to use the son of heaven to command the nobles, rallying various forces in the martial arts world to restore the Tang Dynasty. The benevolent and the tyrannical will clash in this vortex of power! The tomb of the Imperial Concubine and Chang'an City tell the story of the glorious Tang Dynasty; Miao witchcraft and Xiangxi corpse driving reveal the unknown struggles and conflicts in the martial arts world.\n\n(Source: Tencent, translated)",
